data.description: Tree lined street with a pool and park like setting make this 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom, 1 car garage condo a place to call home. Freshly painted interior and brand new carpet. Large walk in closet in one of the bedrooms and two hall closets for storage. Garage offers locked storage cabinets. All appliances are included. Conveniently located close to shopping and I-80. HOA pays water and maintains the exterior of the home.
